snippet.textDisplay: Good info.  Question: Did the HCQ arm of the trial include increased Zinc dosing?  HCQ is an ionophore for Zinc that may reduce replication.  It would be ineffective without Zinc.  Most trials assess HCQ alone and that is not the usage that is recommended in HCQ protocols.
